
    <html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" 
          xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" 
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40">
    <head>
        <title>Project Design - Proposed Solution Details</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #2d2724;
                background-color: #faf6eb;
                margin: 20px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                color: #c05c46;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #2d2724;
                padding-bottom: 5px;
            }
            h2, h3, h4 {
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                color: #2d2724;
            }
            table {
                width: 100%;
                border-collapse: collapse;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
            th, td {
                border: 2px solid #2d2724;
                padding: 10px;
                text-align: left;
            }
            th {
                background-color: #dda15e;
                color: #2d2724;
                font-weight: bold;
            }
            .meta-table {
                width: 50%;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }
            .meta-table th {
                background-color: #2d2724;
                color: #faf6eb;
            }
            .highlight {
                background-color: #faf6eb;
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                padding: 2px 5px;
                border: 1px solid #2d2724;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Project Design - Proposed Solution Details</h1>
        <table class="meta-table">
            <tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Value</th></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Date</b></td><td>11 July 2026</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Team ID</b></td><td>TEAM-MERN-03</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Project Name</b></td><td>ShopEZ - Vintage Sepia Neubrutalist E-Commerce Platform</td></tr>
        </table>
        
    <h2>Proposed Solution Template Details</h2>
    <table>
        <tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Details & Descriptions</th></tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>Problem Statement</b></td>
            <td>Vintage collectors lack e-commerce sites matching the nostalgic theme of their hobbies, while seller dashboards lack simple metrics and inventory alerts.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>Idea / Solution Description</b></td>
            <td>ShopEZ: A vintage sepia neubrutalist portal equipped with monospaced details, a virtual credit card checkout simulator, and metric dashboards with low-stock trackers.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>Novelty / Uniqueness</b></td>
            <td>A 3D flipping card form that visualizes data in real-time, accompanied by a retro secure authorization console showing mainframe log steps.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>Customer Satisfaction</b></td>
            <td>Tactile UI animations (depressing buttons, scanlines) provide a pleasant, satisfying shopping experience.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>Business Model</b></td>
            <td>Commission transaction fees from sellers, along with premium listing slot advertising.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td><b>Scalability</b></td>
            <td>Full decoupled REST controllers and modular schema validators make adding features (e.g. shipping carriers or reviews) seamless.</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    </body>
    </html>
    